image_analysis.description: A photograph of an Apple iMac computer sitting on a reddish-brown glossy desk. The computer screen is on, displaying the macOS desktop with a mountain wallpaper (macOS Sierra). A 'System Preferences' window is open in the center of the screen. To the left of the computer is a bottle of hand sanitizer and a wooden box. To the right, a pen holder and a blue passport are partially visible. A white coiled cord is visible in the bottom left foreground.
image_analysis.layout: Central focus on the computer monitor, with desk accessories in the periphery.
